description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30-Minute Full-Body Strength-Training Workout With Weights' from the channel PS Fit .
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Get ready for a full-body strength-training workout with Nike Global Master Trainer Betina Gozo. This workout includes circuits to work every muscle. Grab a pair of medium weights, anywhere from 8 to 20 pounds, and get ready for a challenge with a series of exercises including tempo squats, single-leg deadlifts, and skaters. After this workout, you'll feel strong, sculpted, and just the right amount of sore.

Find more from Betina on:
